	<content contentuid="hb605530ag8fd0g4ffegb784gc1cfc5a11219" version="6">What exactly are you asking me to do?</content>

	<content contentuid="hda138fabgc01fg4f68gb500g9566c1ab76bb" version="2">What can we do to stop this?</content>

	<content contentuid="ha41c453eg5f6fg4c11g80eeg2580f2358a85" version="1">I'm afraid the power to remove this parasite eludes me. I can't cure us.</content>

	<content contentuid="h8a9f1d9egca6ag4ac3gba63ga7d51d7219cc" version="4">Stand back. Let me see.</content>

	<content contentuid="h5df45ab1gf313g4791g940agcc3a8eaff159" version="3">Apology accepted. Who knows, I might have done the same were the roles reversed.</content>

	<content contentuid="h229baa63g3eb5g4fbcg909dgdf2e72674486" version="3">It's not enough to fight. You people are going to win.</content>

	<content contentuid="hbb0b283bgb773g4770g84fag8ff8af0f6ff7" version="4">I'll speak to Zevlor.</content>

	<content contentuid="h048166ffge6a8g4ccegb166gcb95bc389a12" version="10">Can you help me change my class?</content>
	
	<content contentuid="h2868412cgd8c7g478dgb0c7gfa999c7ad2f5" version="2">A mind flayer?! Give me one reason not to kill you.</content>

	<content contentuid="h4796d248g18beg41a0g9b4dg366d28618c8d" version="3">I found them. They didn't make it, Arabella...</content>

	<content contentuid="he990c3e4ge94fg421ag9b58gbd1ee7280c43" version="2">That's exactly what I plan on doing.</content>

